english spanish and portuguese was signed by lt gen leopoldo 
cintras frias of cuba commander of cuban and angolan troops col 
antonio jose maria the angolan presidential secretary for defense 
and security and maj gen willie meyer commanding officer of the 
southwest african territorial force 
the accord is part of an overall agreement among the three 
nations calling for south african troops to withdraw from angola by 
sept 1 for independence to begin for the south africancontrolled 
territory of southwest africa also known as namibia by nov 1 
