feed store about a mile from the prison six weeks later 
aldersons warden is ronald burkhart at some federal prisons 
he says you can cut the tension with a knife 
here the tone is more relaxed he says i dont want it 
to be tense 
hes speaking in his office on a humid 90degree day hotter 
inside the warden has his tie knotted his suit coat on and the 
