editors note stew leonard runs a happy carnival of a store 
and he usually plays to a full house in transforming a plain dairy 
into a kind of grocery disneyland he set the bottom line to 
dancing his other secret is chiseled on a big rock for all to see 
and he practices it to the letter 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
