said 
the 27yearold woman from gastonia nc spent 2 months in a 
coma following a traffic accident in february 1987 while driving 
to get horse feed she was struck by a drunken driver in bessemer 
city nc 
for the past 10 months she has participated in music therapy 
under the direction of hutchins a singersongwriter and former 
