outstanding balances of all delinquent loans which then totaled 
more than 32 million and with more delinquencies could have 
increased to the full amount of the loans 
rockwood sued ef hutton mortgage corp alleging 
noncompliance and violations of the surety bond and asking the 
court to declare the bond void and unenforceable 
